cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with generating natural language descriptions of images and their regions, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses neural networks for alignment and generation, which falls under machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI). Finally, the paper involves retrieval experiments, which could be considered information retrieval (IR).
